%N A012477 a(n) = (2*n+1) [x^(2*n+1)] arctanh(cos(x)*sin(x)).
%F A012477 Lim sup n->infinity |a(n)|/(2^(4*n+3)*(2*n)!/(Pi^2 + 4*(log(2+sqrt(3)))^2)^(n+1/2)) = 1. - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Oct 24 2013
%F A012477 A(0,k) = 1 and A(n,k) = k*(k+1) * A(n-1,k+2) - 4*k^2 * A(n-1,k) for n > 0. a(n) = A(n,1). - _Seiichi Manyama_, Apr 16 2026
%e A012477 arctanh(cos(x)*sin(x)) = x - 2/3!*x^3 - 40/5!*x^5 + 208/7!*x^7 + 64640/9!*x^9 ...
%t A012477 Table[n!*SeriesCoefficient[ArcTanh[Cos[x]*Sin[x]],{x,0,n}],{n,1,40,2}] (* _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Oct 24 2013 *)
%o A012477 (PARI) a(n, k=1) = if(n==0, 1, k*(k+1)*a(n-1, k+2)-4*k^2*a(n-1, k)); \\ _Seiichi Manyama_, Apr 16 2026
